HEADWORD: Acroteleutic
<hw>Ac`ro*te*leu"tic</hw>
<pr>(⟦acr⟧k`r⟦osl⟧*t⟦esl⟧*l⟦umac⟧"t⟦icr⟧k)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
